data.description: Welcome to 6416 Lincoln Avenue, conveniently situated on Evansville's Eastside close to shopping and schools. This charming Bedford Stone side home boasts 4 bedrooms, 1.5 baths, and an expansive 1500+ square feet of living space. Inside, the living area and three of the bedrooms showcase stunning hardwood floors, while the kitchen and laundry room feature brand new Luxury Vinyl flooring. The updated kitchen offers ample cabinet space, abundant countertop area, and includes modern appliances such as a Range/oven, dishwasher, and microwave oven. Recently updated in September 2020 by JE Scheckel, the HVAC system guarantees comfort with its high-efficiency Gas furnace and Central Air Conditioner by Carrier, complete with a 10-year parts and 5-year labor warranty. Additionally, enjoy the convenience of a programmable thermostat and an Aprilaire electric air filter system. The spacious fourth bedroom, measuring 20x11, could serve as a master suite or an ideal in-law apartment, featuring an adjoining half bath and a private entrance. The backyard is generously sized and securely fenced, providing a safe and enjoyable space for children and pets. The roof, replaced in 2012 by Lang Brothers, boasts a durable dimensional shingle roof
